{"tid":2281851,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"邊個係小編？","createTime":"2020-11-11T11:47:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T14:32:25.000Z","uid":63482,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c07955aab5a8bf5e94ee5dda8b7a8724c5624f","tid":2281851,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T11:47:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>小編</strong> -　<em>屬於編輯嘅自我謙稱</em>。<br />\n<br />\n就好似啲有禮貌嘅人謙稱自己做「鄙人」；<br />\n公司出文案會寫自己做「敝公司」；<br />\n或者資歷比較淺既人會謙稱自己做「小弟」。（仲有好多其它例子）<br />\n<br />\n上述都係屬於自我謙稱，用錯就會好奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n小弟嘗試舉個依家好少人用嘅例子去突出錯用嘅荒謬之處：<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n你老豆：「犬兒初出茅廬，還望多多指教」<br />\n對家長輩：「你『犬兒』昂藏七尺，可以單手游出公海，我當然會多多關照。」<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n如果將他人用作謙稱嘅詞彙，反用嚟稱呼對方，就會有貶低對方嘅感覺。<br />\n用錯咗，亦都被人覺得你無禮貌／中文唔太好。<br />\n<br />\n利申：純粹成日見到有人喺FB留言話:「『小編』真係點點點/ 『小編』可唔可以提供多啲資訊?」有感而發。希望唔好咁多人用錯。"},{"pid":"2ab7e1d5a37a5f2af9c872fe7c5948ad37acbd06","tid":2281851,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T12:30:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"431e2a9e6ad482c0fa8dd63183996a3d4f22d56c","tid":2281851,"uid":360800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"FB專頁啲所謂編緝仔，想聽人地叫你編緝？<br />\n配唔配啊？笑撚死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9439397ecbd94ad2cadeb1fc4c431eed82934ece","tid":2281851,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"431e2a9e6ad482c0fa8dd63183996a3d4f22d56c","tid":2281851,"uid":360800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"FB專頁啲所謂編緝仔，想聽人地叫你編緝？<br />\n配唔配啊？笑撚死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"我通常都會叫佢地admin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為佢地好多錯字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}